message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11,000. This is a great deal considering its value. Let me know what you think!
Alice, I appreciate the offer but $11,000 is a bit too high for me. I'm willing to pay $9,500 for the product.  Let me know what you think.

Bob, thanks for the counteroffer.  While I appreciate your interest, $9,500 is a bit too low for me.  I'm willing to come down to $10,500.  This is a fair price considering the value of the product.  Let's see if we can make this work!
